title: Bio Asia Pacific
description: Bio Asia Pacific is the new leading conference and exhibition platform for Biotechnology, Life Sciences and Smart Health in Asia Pacific. Bio Asia Pacific is focusing on innovative therapeutics and healthcare services blending 21st century Life Sciences with latest in technology. Experience thought leadership and cutting-edge products in Life Sciences, Bio Tech, Med Tech, Digital Health, Precision Medicine, Biopharma and Preventive Health in an inspiring event format with the innovation showcases and knowledge seminars. Bio Asia Pacific will co-locate with Thailand LAB INTERNATIONAL.
